      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_17",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "EMMA GRIFFIN WITCH ON PARANORMAL POWER",
        "bbox": [
          0.17929759706398551,
          0.8908730159586927,
          0.2735674644886947,
          0.9069940476587184
        ],
        "order": 32
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_30",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "·Follow Emma at instagram.com/ emmagriffinwitch. Her book, The Witch's Way Home, is out now",
        "bbox": [
          0.7800369695601082,
          0.908430232892621,
          0.9537892763425412,
          0.9374999997694745
        ],
        "order": 33
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_18",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Determined to help, her mum confessed she was actually a sorceress and would teach Emma the skills to prove the reader wrong. In 1999, Emma and Steve had",
        "bbox": [
          0.059149723338137714,
          0.909883720979072,
          0.1626617382145425,
          0.9201388888607197
        ],
        "order": 34
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_32",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "features@mirror.co.uk X@DailyMirror",
        "bbox": [
          0.8632162640235888,
          0.9389534886042852,
          0.9537892782540396,
          0.9549418602510927
        ],
        "order": 36
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_22",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "She became a full-time witch around five years ago and initiated nursery manager Holly as a sea witch in 2021, making a third generation of witches in her family.",
        "bbox": [
          0.24214418299636878,
          0.9491279069831902,
          0.40665433832217707,
