      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "\"My first time was at Hampton Court, but ever since then, it's happened regularly. My younger brother Ben and I knew our parents were different, but then, aren't evervone's?\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.04805914982416401,
          0.4461805556236747,
          0.18302503408173082,
          0.5236200916378334
        ],
        "order": 14
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "She says she inherited her mum's magical powers and \"came out of the closet - the broom closet\" after her parents died from cancer in 2019 and 2020.",
        "bbox": [
          0.04805915014203001,
          0.5260416667040044,
          0.21811460481509135,
          0.5741567459140662
        ],
        "order": 15
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_11",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "he is now a full-time witch, cine reading\". She says: \"I'm the real-life Molly Weasley. Everyone calls me that.\"",
        "bbox": [
          0.048059147393069754,
          0.5857558141910705,
          0.20887245809815427,
          0.6528571348523083
        ],
        "order": 17
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_12",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "But, unlike the Harry Potter witch, she is a thoroughly modern Molly, with 96,000 followers on Instagram and 40,000 on TikTok.",
        "bbox": [
          0.04795693578040092,
          0.6540178571213549,
          0.16266173886149257,
          0.722790142622682
        ],
        "order": 18
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_029_13",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "And she recently cast her spell on 262 would-be magic makers from across the world, initiating them as witches in one big, free Zoom session.",
        "bbox": [
          0.048059147482820926,
          0.723837209661032,
          0.1682070227465343,
          0.7921626984242
        ],
        "order": 19
      }
    ]
  },
